      <head>Nathan Broder</head>

      <div>
        <p>American editor and musicologist, associate editor of <title level="j">The
            Musical Quarterly</title> 1945-67; he was involved editorially with New York publishers
            G. Schirmer and W. W. Norton, and taught at Columbia University (1946-62).</p>
        
        <p>There is no correspondence between Schenker and Broder; he wrote an article jointly with
        Arthur Waldeck on Schenker's theory.</p>
      </div>
